## Interface: 120000
## Title: PIority
## Notes: PIority takes the guesswork out of Power Infusion targeting. Scans your party or raid, ranks every DPS/tank spec by PI value, and lets you click any row to instantly update your PI_H macro. Features auto-pick mode, item level display, addon-presence detection, PI request notifications, persistent layout, and slash commands (/pi, /pirequest).
